; Installscript V.1.0 for Amiga4ever 4 
; © 1998 by : RT the Machine

smp installmod
copy C/Wait to SYS:C/Wait
wait 2
Echo "         Amiga 4ever Ausgabe:4 !           "
Echo "    -- Installation auf Festplatte -- "
Echo " "
Wait 2
Echo " "
Echo "   Erstelle Schublade... "
Echo " "
wait 1
makedir SYS:Amiga4ever
makedir SYS:Amiga4ever/c
makedir SYS:Amiga4ever/libs
Copy Amiga4ever.i to SYS:Amiga4ever.info
wait 4
Echo " "
Echo "   Kopiere die benötigten C-Befehle... "
Echo " "
wait 1
Copy C/amfmplay to SYS:Amiga4ever/c/amfmplay
Copy C/Smp to SYS:Amiga4ever/c/Smp
Copy C/More to SYS:Amiga4ever/C/More
Copy C/PPshow to SYS:Amiga4ever/C/PPshow
Copy C/Run to SYS:Amiga4ever/C/Run
Copy c/echo to SYS:Amiga4ever/c/echo
Copy C/PR-Infos.lha to SYS:Amiga4ever/c/PR-Infos.lha
wait 4
Echo " "
Echo "   Kopiere die Medplayer.library..."
Echo " "
Copy libs/medplayer.library to SYS:libs/medplayer.library
Copy libs/medplayer.library to SYS:Amiga4ever/libs/medplayer.library
wait 3
Echo " "
Echo "   Kopiere die Musikmodule... "
Echo " "
wait 6
Copy c/M1 to SYS:Amiga4ever/c/M1
Copy c/M2 to SYS:Amiga4ever/c/M2
wait 3
Echo " "
Echo "   Kopiere die Bilder... "
Echo " "
wait 1
Copy c/pic to SYS:Amiga4ever/c/pic
Copy c/picX to SYS:Amiga4ever/c/picX
Copy c/pic2 to SYS:Amiga4ever/c/pic2
Copy c/pic3 to SYS:Amiga4ever/c/pic3
Copy c/pic4 to SYS:Amiga4ever/c/pic4
Copy c/pic5 to SYS:Amiga4ever/c/pic5
Copy c/pic6 to SYS:Amiga4ever/c/pic6
Copy c/pic7 to SYS:Amiga4ever/c/pic7
wait 6
Echo " "
Echo "   Kopiere das Magazin... "
Echo " "
wait 4
Copy Amiga4ever_Ausg.4 to SYS:Amiga4ever/Amiga4ever_Ausg.4
Copy Amiga4ever_Ausg.4.i to SYS:Amiga4ever/Amiga4ever_Ausg.4.info
Copy Amiga4ever.Ausg.4.guide to SYS:Amiga4ever/Amiga4ever.Ausg.4.guide
Copy Informationen to SYS:Amiga4ever/Informationen
Copy Informationen.i to SYS:Amiga4ever/Informationen.info
Copy MachMit!!! to SYS:Amiga4ever/MachMit!!!
Copy MachMit!!!.i to SYS:Amiga4ever/MachMit!!!.info
Copy Die4everCharts to SYS:Amiga4ever/Die4everCharts
Copy Die4everCharts.i to SYS:Amiga4ever/Die4everCharts.info
wait 9
Echo " "
Echo "   Installation fertig !"
Echo "   Viel Vergnügen beim lesen..."
wait 1
stopsmp installmod
wait 2